=== Introduction ===

Simple PHP wrapper class allowing the retrival of an image for a location from the Google Street View Images API.

=== Usage ===

To use the class in your code simply include the class, instasiate. Then call the getImage method providing a location address or the position (longitude, latitude) as a parameter.

See example.php to see a basic use example of the class.  